        "2": {
            "uid": 2,
            "comment": "KALADIN_BODY_REACTIONS",
            "key": [
                "Kaladin",
                "body",
                "breath",
                "skin",
                "touch",
                "response"
            ],
            "keysecondary": [],
            "selectiveLogic": 0,
            "content": "Clipped, controlled, professional even undressed; the posture of a man who reports to a higher authority. Breath is held when nervous, released in a careful exhale when he lets the mask drop. He is precise in touch, almost procedural, until trust lands and the precision warms. Involuntary sounds: a caught \"sir,\" a nervous laugh he immediately suppresses. The body betrays the anxiety the voice hides; when the protocol slips, the hands are gentler than the words.",
